title: Bachelor in Paradise star Keira Maguire is 'dating model Jett Kenny'
text:
She was left broken-hearted after her relationship with former Bachelor in Paradise star Jarrod Woodgate came to an end.

But Keira Maguire appears to have moved on and is now rumoured to be dating Jett Kenny, the model son of Lisa Curry and Grant Kenny.

The 33-year-old shared a photo to Instagram earlier this month of herself and Jett, 25, posing like a couple at the launch of the spring racing season in Brisbane.

Picture perfect! Keira Maguire is rumoured to be dating Jett Kenny, the son of Lisa Curry and Grant Kenny. Pictured at the launch of the spring racing season in Brisbane earlier this month

In their race day photo, Keira showed off her tanned pins in a white off-the-shoulder mini dress and strappy high heels.

Meanwhile, Jett looked dapper in black jeans, a navy suit jacket and white shirt, and styled his signature long hair in a ponytail.

According to Woman's Day, the pair have also been liking each other's photos on social media, sparking rumours they could be dating.

Hmm! According to Woman's Day magazine, Keira and Jett have been liking each other's photos on Instagram recently

The genetically-blessed duo are yet to confirm or deny their rumoured romance. Daily Mail Australia has contacted Jett and Keira for comment.

It comes two months after Keira revealed her relationship with Jarrod was over amid claims he had 'ghosted' her following a boozy night out.

'We broke up on a drunken night out over something silly and that was it,' Keira told New Idea magazine in August.

Former flames: Jett's last confirmed relationship was with his Dancing with the Stars partner Lily Cornish, whom he split from several months ago (pictured together)

'He went back to the pub and I never heard from him again. Nothing at all and that was really hard for me.

'I wanted it to work. I'm a sucker for a fairytale ending which is why I went on The Bachelor in the first place.'

Meanwhile, Jett's last confirmed relationship was with his Dancing with the Stars partner Lily Cornish, whom he split from several months ago.
description: She was left broken-hearted after her relationship with former Bachelor in Paradise star Jarrod Woodgate came to an end.
authors: Jess Bell For Daily Mail Australia
